"The ``fw`` health reporter tracks FW crashes. Dumping the reporter will show "
"the core dump of the most recent FW crash, and if no FW crash has happened "
"since power cycle - a snapshot of the FW memory. Diagnose callback shows FW "
"uptime based on the most recently received heartbeat message (the crashes "
